{"tid":279723,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch遊戲］ 有什麼Party Games 最好玩😍？","createTime":"2017-06-11T13:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T16:08:41.000Z","uid":54235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eac712b5dde81a5e0d979b914d6d594265b618d9","tid":279723,"uid":54235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"Bomberman ?<br />\n孖寶？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fd8c34a915e7bb03c9d6b71673a452ae44261f","tid":279723,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"唔好買炸彈就得  <br />\n<br />\n孖車  12  arms  都得"},{"pid":"ce83b42d49704c2eb8f562a16be54fc5e8da82a3","tid":279723,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"炸彈不知幾爽 4條友互片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0477cc82bd20b294f07cc0a0d271e1df50fc41","tid":279723,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"孖車就唔駛講啦<br />\n<br />\nSuper Bomberman R<br />\n單機雙打或Online打ok<br />\n但你預道具唔算多款<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係<br />\n要打故事同online先賺到game內既錢黎買對戰地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知幾時先開得哂D對戰地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故事玩完三個星球<br />\n我先發現可按實L/R掣黎轉視點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n故事預設斜視點唔好睇改番中間視點易玩D<br />\n故事單打偏難玩<br />\n可以雙打合作玩既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSnipperclips<br />\n呢隻兩個角色互剪身體合作puzzle動作game<br />\n出奇地搞笑<br />\n唔好比D低B畫風呃左你以為唔好玩<br />\n上Youtube搵D coop片睇你先明點解好笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNBA Playgrounds<br />\nNBA Jam進化版<br />\n單機雙打唔錯易上手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUltra Street Fighter II: The Final Challengers <br />\n街霸2第N個加強版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫做係第一隻手提遊戲機高清版街霸2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定價係貴<br />\n但最近跌到$185蚊<br />\n街霸2本身係好好既對戰game<br />\n係歷久不衰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果等得<br />\n黎緊ARMS、柒彈2其實都好適合party玩<br />\nARMS有個排球mode睇落幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實你有部機<br />\n自己上日本同美國eShop都睇得哂有乜game啦<br />\n好多都有片睇<br />\n睇一陣gameplay片<br />\n都唔難分到係咪正既party game"},{"pid":"62c04f930267a726686c7284e18bf1d7c5fee0f6","tid":279723,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炸彈不知幾爽 4條友互片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炸彈人同真人對戰樂趣依舊唔差<br />\n只係要賺大量coins先買到新對戰地圖好on9"},{"pid":"690367aae93a33ed39c99c6e2bbb1f79fd5a49a5","tid":279723,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"arms再買多對joy con <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 我就唔會買多對joy con,平時女友用pro掣,我拆對joy con出黎就夠用"},{"pid":"be26f784c35033cb82c58773a23df1c383501017","tid":279723,"uid":108833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:08:41.000Z","msg":"一定係依隻。。。不過冇出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://nintendoswitchonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/mario-sports-superstars-nintendo-816x459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnintendoswitchonline.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fmario-sports-superstars-nintendo-816x459.jpg&h=aa63121f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}